            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini Dei eterni, anno incarnationis eius millesimo centesimo
                        septuagesimo, VIII idus madii, indictione III. Manifesti sumus nos
                                <persName><name ref="Berardinus">Berardinus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Malapetha">Malepethe</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName> iugalis eius et
                        filia <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> quia comuniter
                        (…) ubi interesse (vi)detur notitia duorum meorum propinquorum, videlicet
                                <persName><name ref="Lotteringus">Lotteringi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidonis</name></persName> germanorum
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Albertinus">Albertini</name></persName>, (…)
                        per hanc cartulam damus et tradimus tibi Deo et <orgName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals">ospitali</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Teupasci</placeName></orgName> tres nostras petias de terra partim pro
                        pretio, partim pro remedio animarum nostrarum. Que sunt in <rs
                            key="#Seigneurial_district">districhto</rs> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3237" key="#Seigneurial_district">Paule</placeName>, quarum
                        una tenet unum caput in <placeName ref="#places/3237">Podio
                            Corioli</placeName> et aliud caput in rivo, unum latum in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Tafurellus">Tafurelli</name></persName> et
                        aliud latus in <rs key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">terra Paganinga</rs>.
                        Et alie que sunt in alio podio (…), quarum una tenet unum caput in via et
                        aliud caput in fossa, et latus in terra <persName><name ref="Bernarduccius"
                                >Bernarducii</name></persName> et alia petia a duabus partibus est
                        terra predicti Bernarducii in eodem podio. (…) Pro qua nostra datione
                        pretium recepimus a predicto ospitale sol. decem (…).
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) et insuper penam XX sol. Actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/217">Montis Cuccari</placeName>. Signa manuum
                        suprascriptorum iugalium (…). <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Calvus"
                                >Calvettus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannis</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rienis">Rienis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rainuccius">Ranucius</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Arturus">Arturetti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Et prefati iugales precipierunt <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Ragibodus">Rambotto</name></persName>,
                        qui mitteret in posessionem illius ospitalis rectorem. (S) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Bonaccursus"
                            >Bonacursus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> apostolice sedis post traditam
                        complevi et dedi.</ab>
